abstract: NFL Roundup; Indianapolis Colts quarterback Andrew Luck practices with team but will not play in game against Houston Texans; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: The Colts’ Luck and the Broncos’ Manning made progress in their recoveries from injuries, but their teams plan to stick with backup quarterbacks on Sunday.

headline.main: Andrew Luck and Peyton Manning Practice, but Won’t Start
headline.print_headline: Luck and Manning Practice, but Won’t Start
